import_SigProfiler

Source: R/import_functions.R
import_SigProfiler.Rd

import_SigProfiler

import_SigProfiler(folder = ".")

Arguments

folder

a folder containing SigProfilerExtractor results

Value

A list of tibbles containing the SigProfiler activity matrices

Examples

#Import dummy SigProfilerExtractor output results
SPfolder = system.file("extdata", "SP", package = "sigvar")
Qlist = import_SigProfiler(SPfolder)
